grid.text: Third pine. Waki stands up, and goes to 9. First pine. Waki tsure turns facing stage and goes to 5.

captions.translation: [WAKI] At this point, in any case, Munechika
captions.transcription: [WAKI] Kono ue wa tonimo kakunimo Munechika ga,

captions.translation: must here decide his course of action.
Like the ripples beaten along a well-forged blade, his heart wavers.
captions.transcription: Mitsurugi no yaiba no midaruru kokoro narikeri.

captions.translation: Yet, as the reign in the present age is righteous,
captions.transcription: Sarinagara goseitÅ sugunaru ima no miyo nareba,

captions.translation: a miracle may well be afforded me.
I must place my trust only in this.
I must place my trust only in this.
